{"declarations":[{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Std/Time/Zoned/Database/PosixTz.html#Std.Time.TimeZone.parsePosixTz\"><span class=\"name\">Std</span>.<span class=\"name\">Time</span>.<span class=\"name\">TimeZone</span>.<span class=\"name\">parsePosixTz</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">s</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#String\">String</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">extended</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool\">Bool</a> := <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool.false\">false</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Except\">Except</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#String\">String</a> <a href=\"./Std/Time/Zoned/RecurringRule.html#Std.Time.TimeZone.RecurringRule\">RecurringRule</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Parse a POSIX TZ footer string into a `RecurringRule`, returning an error on failure.\n\nWhen `extended` is `true`, transition times accept signed hours in the range\n-`167` to `167` instead of the POSIX-required 0 to `24` (TZif version 3+).\n","docLink":"./Std/Time/Zoned/Database/PosixTz.html#Std.Time.TimeZone.parsePosixTz","kind":"def","line":166,"name":"Std.Time.TimeZone.parsePosixTz","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/62eed1db4d67327ec8120be05f1a1b0847d74561/src/Std/Time/Zoned/Database/PosixTz.lean#L166-L174"}}],"imports":["Std.Internal.Parsec","Std.Time.Zoned.ZoneRules"],"instances":[],"name":"Std.Time.Zoned.Database.PosixTz"}